'''Tôn Hiếu Anh''' is a Vietnamese [[fashion design]]er, and editor and producer of Fashion Studio on [[Vietnam Television|VTV6]] (Television Program).<ref>[http://giaitri.vnexpress.net/tin-tuc/thoi-trang/bo-suu-tap/ton-hieu-anh-nhieu-nguoi-tiec-cho-toi-1882976.html Tôn Hiếu Anh: 'Nhiều người tiếc cho tôi']</ref>

He was a model from 1994 to 2000, then moved into design, winning the 2nd prize of fashion contest 24/7 of the [[British Council]] in 2002, and 1st prize of Dep Fair 2005.

